{"tid":1971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"容議員好pure好true：記者會？乜記者要開會㗎？","createTime":"2016-11-25T17:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-25T17:52:55.000Z","uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6e49926a642f076e9a16c1c9ac724f5e3fb549a","tid":1971,"uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:40:25.000Z","msg":"喺選舉論壇上以答非所問而一鳴驚人嘅新民黨立法會議員容海恩，上任後繼續發揮「不如你話畀我知吖」嘅精神，八方同事喺立法會做嘢時，咁啱同佢同lift，容好親切咁問lift入面一位政治行家去邊，行家答「去9樓有個記者會呀」，容議員唔知係無知定可愛，問行家「記者會？&hellip;&hellip;乜記者要開會㗎？」<br />\n<br />\n八方同事形容當時大家都呆咗，難得行家好禮貌咁解釋，「即係&hellip;&hellip;有個記者招待會&hellip;&hellip;咁&hellip;&hellip;」容議員「哦」咗一聲就出lift，其間同事竭盡所能忍笑，將尷尬減至最低。可能容議員喺外國讀過吓幾年書，就變咗番書妹唔識中文啩，唔知平日佢黨友約佢一齊開PC，佢會唔會以為係開私人電腦呢？（爛gag出沒注意）<br />\n<br />\nsource :<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161125&amp;guid=55966385&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161125%26guid%3D55966385%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B88W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=0277a1e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161125%26guid%3D55966385%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=f12aaa14\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161125&amp;guid=55966385&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb6b1a1b972e9570426cee0a1b208f82b5fb845","tid":1971,"uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:41:28.000Z","msg":"貼下啲新聞先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941b48995f7ca3c201a8b0fc4124ce9f0bb20a45","tid":1971,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:42:39.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾"},{"pid":"624e7383938655978821c6f8e32e504d15ae2874","tid":1971,"uid":5489,"